===Microphone placement===
'''Each technique begins with a bullet point'''
====Acoustic guitar====
*Place an omnidirectional microphone near the sound hole. <ref name="REHBpg152">The Recording Engineers Handbook.Page 152.ISBN 1-93292-900-2</ref>
*Place a microphone aimed where the fret board meets the body and move it 8 inches back away from the guitar.<ref name="REHBpg152"></ref>
*Aim a stereo mic with one capsule pointed at the bridge and the other at the headstock<ref name="REHBpg152"></ref>
